<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Spell: Zurnaik`s Animation</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
MAGIC ITEM <br>
Level Needed: 55<br>
Skill: Conjuration   <br>
Mana Cost: 350<br>
WT: 0.1   Size: SMALL<br>
Class: ENC <br>
Race: ALL<br>
<br>
Components: a piece of parchment, a quill, finnok`s treatise page #2 (left), finnok`s treatise page #2 (right)<br>
In: phantasmal tome<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Yield:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 1<br>
This combine may only be made by Enchanters  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bregaladlow>Bregalad LoW</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Enchanter Realm Member</span><br>  Posts: 119<br> <font color=#330000>(8/4/03 12:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Zumaik's Animation</span><hr size=1> Unfortunately, one of the Finnok 2 parts also goes into some very nice priest spells...  and is insanely rare to boot.  I have several copies of one part, but never saw the other on bazaar or dropped.  That said, Juggs camp in Sebilis is your best bet.<br>
<br>
Great thing about this animation  is it comes already dual wielding, which is very convenient - and it does have improvement over Kintaz, especially HP-wize.   Also, it's a long road from 55 to 62, believe me.  I suggest checking bazaar often - price fluctuates, sometimes you can get a much better deal. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Phantasmist, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
